  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC263">
          <l>eṟṟeṉ kiḷavi yiṟanta poruṭṭē.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/163/mode/1up">163</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/164/mode/1up">164</ref>.</p>
      <p>
iccūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ituvum tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷceykuvaṉavaṟṟiṉmēl uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
urai: eṟṟu eṉpatu iṟantaporuḷ viḷakki niṟkum eṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC263-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘eṟṟeṉ ṉuṭampi ṉeḻiṉalam’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC263-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘eṟṟēṟṟa millāruḷ yāṉēṟṟa millātēṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatum atu. iḵtu irakkap poruḷ mēṟṟu eṉpatu.   (15)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n214/mode/1up">211</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i–ḷ. eṟṟeṉṉuñcol iṟantaporuṇmaittu. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u - m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC263-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘eṟṟeṉ ṉuṭampi ṉeḻiṉalam’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu eṉṉalamiṟantateṉṉum poruḷpaṭa niṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC263-Cena-cit2">
        <l>‘eṟṟēṟṟa millāruḷ yāṉēṟṟa millātēṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatūum itupoḻutu tuṇivillāruṭṭuṇivillātēṉ yāṉ eṉṟu tuṇiviṟanta teṉpatu paṭa niṉṟatu.	(15)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/293/mode/1up">293</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, poruḷpaṭumāṟu kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i–ḷ) eṟṟeṉ kiḷavi yiṟanta poruṭṭē ― eṟṟeṉṉuñ col loṉṟi ṉiṭattuniṉṟu moṉṟu pōyiṟṟeṉṉum poruṇmai yuṇarttutal uṭaitteṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u–m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC263-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>eṟṟe ṉuṭampi ṉeḻilnalam.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
iḵteṉṉeḻi ṉalamiṟanta teṉa niṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC263-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘eṟṟēṟṟa millāruḷ yāṉēṟṟa millātēṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatūum, itu poḻutu tuṇivillāruṭṭuṇivillātēṉ yāṉ, eṉṟu tuṇivu iṟanta teṉpatupaṭa niṉṟatu.
<term xml:lang="en">(15)</term>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n181/mode/1up">174</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
i–ḷ: ― eṟṟu eṉṉum col kaḻintatu eṉṉum poruṇmai yuṭaittu. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u–m: ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC263-Tey-cit1">
        <l>eṟṟe ṉuṭampi ṉeḻiṉalam</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.	[15]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
